name: tounges out
description: oh to be an alien woman posting a thirst trap on the internet. i've always had such an appeal to purple-ish/pink skin tones, anything that brings the color to a forefront of a drawing!! im sure you can tell i already have a strong affinity of drawing really cute variations of girls !! i think my favorite thing about it is that you can really convey some kind of flavor or feeling depending on the drawing. like this one, this one makes me think about chewing bubblegum on a ufo!!! alien girls must live life so lavishly.
